law.text: This Part V of this subtitle may not be construed to impair or limit the authority granted to the Department of Human Resources, the State Department of Education, or the Department of Health and Mental Hygiene under any other provision of the Code unless that provision necessarily is inconsistent with this Part V of this subtitle.
